.TH HIDLOOM-LEDD 5 "@HIDLOOM_VERSION@" "HIDloom" "File Formats"
.SH NAME
hidloom-ledd \- ledd JSON configuration
.SH DESCRIPTION
The ledd configuration defines LED topology, animation defaults, semantic
roles, direct-frame socket paths, and fallback behavior.
.SH FILES
.TP
.B /usr/lib/hidloom/config/default/ledd.json
Packaged default configuration.
.TP
.B /mnt/p3/led_state.json
Runtime LED state persisted by logicd.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR ledd (8),
.BR logicd (8)
.br
Lighting documentation:
https://github.com/cqa02303/hidloom/tree/@HIDLOOM_GIT_SHA@/docs/lighting
